@startuml
title UC3 — Update Work Order (High-Level)

actor Technician
participant "Maintenance Management System" as MMS
participant "Notification Service" as Notif
actor Supervisor

Technician -> MMS : Update work order
MMS -> Notif : Send completion notification
Notif -> Supervisor : Notify completed work order
MMS --> Technician : Confirm work order updated

@enduml